    "name": "session",
    "purpose": "Owns the agent session runtime, total SessionEvent routing entrypoint, local task-originated event channel, shared session preview context with SessionContext::snapshot for prompt rendering, and task creation. route_session_event routes task, step, execution, and plan events back to the owning Task by task id through the task signature and then calls send_client_event once; send_client_event applies a matches! filter that forwards only Task Status/Preview/CreateFailed and all Step events to the client. Host preview queries build a preview TaskSignature.",
